{
  "stem": "16395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Potatoes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother was very, very religious because she came out from a very religious-- I don't think so my father was that religious, but my mother was very, very religious.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she really-- she waited in the morning before I went to school, I should say the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night I was too tired and I didn't-- and when I went to bed, sometimes I went to bed without saying [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she used to come over to the bed, she says to me, you didn't say the [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And maybe-- maybe God won't give you life next morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got up, I washed my hands, and I used to say [INAUDIBLE] not because I wanted, because I think the way she brought me up, all religious was on fear.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was afraid that I won't wake up, and I was afraid that I won't do good in school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how I said the [INAUDIBLE] and that's how I said [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and Saturday, I wouldn't do anything bad because you know, she watched me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She watched over me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother was really a very good mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She used to that in the morning to all her-- my sisters and help them with the children and-- and then she came home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was really jealous that she is running to the married kids, and-- and she's not with me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I used to say, mommy, when I grow up, I will have only one child, not eight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I won't marry a man older than-- than our father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He will be in the same age.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
